skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: birthday cake time
des:
Next birthday: This skill will tell how many days till your next birthday, and wish you Happy Birthday on your birthday date. 
Zodiac signs: In addition this skill will tell your zodiac signs and your strength based on your zodiac signs.

Launching the skill
---------------------------
"Alexa, Open Birthday Cake Time".
"Alexa, ask Birthday Cake Time when is my birthday".

Interaction with the skill
-------------------------------
"How many days till my birthday".
"When is my next birthday".
"When is my birthday".

Any feedback would be really appreciated.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
